Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.97,0:00:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Princess Celestia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea for\Nyour Onesversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My...Onesversary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.74,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The one thousand one hundred\Neleventh year anniversary
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of when you first\Nraised the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing Pinkie\NPie reminded us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,or we woulda forgot\Nto celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To commemorate your first\Nsunrise, I've written a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to perform it at\Nmy School of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[excited laugh] Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think a play\Nis a fantastic idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she just...\Nprance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Forgive me for\Ngetting so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a filly, my\Nfriends often put on plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was so wonderful;\Neverypony coming together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to create a magical experience\Nto share with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always believed theatre\Nbrings out the best in us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:01:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and forges a special\Nbond of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you used to act!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always too busy\Nwith my magic lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to be part of any\Nplays myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, it's something\NI always wished
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I could experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we would be honored if you\Nwould be the star of our play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,WE WOULD?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to\Nstar in your play!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when did that\Nhappen exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse\Nus for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia has always\Nwanted to be in a play,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and this one's about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But how are we supposed\Nto give her directions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the ruler of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's also our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia's always\Nkind to everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we have a chance to\Nfinally do something for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we should!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, how many times\Nhas Celestia helped us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Guided us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a warm calming\Nvoice over our shoulder-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?\N[startled gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Princess Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your invitation\Nis very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you certain\Nit's wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no acting\Nexperience at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Experience? Pssh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be playing yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll all help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd mean so much\Nto the students
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were in our show.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I would be delighted\Nto join your theatre troupe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Confetti is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wormy applecores, Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told ya\Nto keep your special effects
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,away from my sets?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hundred twenty-seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Unless you just DID.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's three\Nhundred twenty-eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you've memorized\Nyour lines already, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get past terrifying,\Nparalyzing stage fright,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the rest is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I just hope\NPrincess Celestia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,says we can do our play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! As soon as she sees\Nthese fabulous costumes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,all she'll be able\Nto say is 'brava!'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads up!\NHere comes our answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful news, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeeeha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to put on our show?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia is\Ngonna be our star!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's how I felt, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia? Starring in our play?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she was a little\Nnervous at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but I told her not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,With us helping, it'll\Nall go smooth as--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,SILK! [zoom]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find the silk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If Celestia is going\Nto be in our play,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to take everything\Nup to the next level!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,None of these old\Nideas will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Forget my\Nregular party cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For princess-size effects, we're\Ngonna need "Big Bertha!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack: Grrr... PINKIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Our play is gonna be AMAZING!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta tell everypony I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And even the ones I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why in tarnation are y'all\Ngettin' so star-struck?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We've met Princess\NCelestia before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Plenty of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were formal things,\Ngalas, world-saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine doing sweaty\Nwarm-ups with a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Blowing your nose in\Nfront of a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting around just...\Ntalking with a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a princess.\NYou talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a\NPRINCESS princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia wants to experience\Nthe special friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that theatre ponies have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To give her that, you just\Nneed to be yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You...you really\Nthink so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Aw, quit frettin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a coupla\Npals gettin' together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to put on a Onesversary play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What could go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Places, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to rehearse\N"A New Day in Equestria!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Directed, written, and\Nproduced by Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Page 1, Act 1, Scene 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,ACTION!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time,\Nbefore Celestia,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria was suffering\Nterrible hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Raising the sun every\Nmorning was so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it took five great sorcerers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,plus Starswirl the\NBearded to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And every day, the unicorns\Nhelping Starswirl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,would use so much magic,\Nthey lost their powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Things looked bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, Equestria would\Nlose all its magic-users!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the land would be covered\Nin darkness for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can't believe\Nhow good my play is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The sets, the props, the\Noutfits, they're all great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And, here comes\Nthe best part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, a student named\NCelestia discovered she had the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,power to raise the sun herself,\Nwithout draining her magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...that's your\Ncue, Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Right! Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahe-heh-hem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:07:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[soft and awkward]\NIt is time for a new\Nday in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time for a new\Nday in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And your delivery was...great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe you should try\Nit a tiny bit louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For the ponies in\Nthe back row.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes.\NMy Royal Canterlot Voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the\Nreminder, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,IT IS TIME FOR A NEW\NDAY IN EQUESTRIA!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness, this theatre\Ndoes have strong acoustics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still learning to\N"hone my craft."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, you're doing...fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we try it\None more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you're\Ntalking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[robotic] It is time for a\Nnew day in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit more energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[overdone] It's time for a\Nnew day in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe you've\Nnever done this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to\Nthe dance number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Again! Step, buck,\Nleap, touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Step, buck, leap, touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Movin' on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Five, six, seven, eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come ON, StarSWIRL!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw OFF that musty HAT,\Nand let's have a-a dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Our lead actress\Nis a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell Celestia\Nshe's terrible,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll hurt her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be a bad friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I keep her\Nin the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll be the laughing stock\Nof Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be a worse friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya need to tell Celestia\Nthe truth, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other suggestions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just\Ncancel the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,REAL suggestions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, most of\NEquestria doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,even know we're doing\Na Onesversary play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If we shut it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony will ever miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So they'll never find\Nout Princess Celestia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is a bad actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And she won't be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's the\Nperfect plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash: All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just finished telling\Neverypony to come to our play!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You...did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've seen how\Nexcited they got
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,when they found out\NCelestia was in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they'd\Ntell their friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then their friends'd\Ntell their friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony in Equestria\Nis gonna see this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, did I miss something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bright light\Nof hope being snuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't cancel the show,\NI know what I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest with Celestia and give\Nthe lead role to somepony else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:10:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you know truth is\Na huge part of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And so is making another\Npony's dreams come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I promised Celestia\Nthat this time she could
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,be a part of the play\Ninstead of just watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I plan to keep\Nthat promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...how?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: You want to\Ngive me acting lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no no no no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, a special\Nworkshop with other actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To... take your performance\Nfrom good to flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I always knew\Ntheatre must be about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That special stage pony bond\Nof shared trust and honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's\Nwhat it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia? Meet\NMethod Mare performers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On Stage and\NRaspberry Beret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Avec pleasure,\NYour Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The pleasure is all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything\NI can do to become
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a better Equestrian\Nthespian, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought we'd make\Nit up as we go along. Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise known as [bad French\Naccent] "improvisation!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,YES, and we can start as soon\Nas we get out of this box!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What.. box?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. How's it going over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That sun will\Nnever rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I have\Nsomething even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity: Oh! It's the\Nperfect substitute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the perfect substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me something\Nto be happy about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try visualization!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you're skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's so\Nsnowy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Brrr...I'm\Ngetting chilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I get you a blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ponyville Express\Nis leaving the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,WOO WOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,CHUGGA CHUGGA CHUGGA CHUGGA!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It is? I don't\Nsee anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be weeping\Nwillows in the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We are strong in adversity,\Nyet supple as we bow to fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The classroom floor\Nunder my hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that count?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,PINKIE PIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's realistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is just like\Na burning marshmallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: What are\Nthey doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] The simplest acting exercise\Nthey could think of:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A game of Charades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Actor: A puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A duck-billed platypus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Antidisestablishmentarianism!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I give up! What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My love for Equestria\Nand all the ponies in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you felt what I\Nwas emoting, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's the best\Nacting we've seen all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. I tried, and\Ntried, and tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to face facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't make\NCelestia an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's only one\Nthing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her the\Ntruth? Finally?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've re-written the script\Nto give Celestia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a more "artistic" part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With no lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And to make sure\Nthe show's a hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've whipped up the\Nbiggest, bestest,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,flashiest fake sun EVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[groan] Pinkie, that\Nlooks...unsafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would untested magic\Nfireworks that I bought in a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,back alley from Trixie\Nat midnight be unsafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T TAKE IT ANYMORE!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,IT WAS SUPPOSED TO\NBE A SIMPLE PLAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,JUST ONE SIMPLE PLAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,AND THEN EVERYTHING GOES WRONG!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,FROM THE STAGE, TO\NTHE PROPS, RIGHT DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,TO THE WORST LEAD\NACTRESS IN EQUESTRIA!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you honestly felt I was a bad\Nactress, why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to\Ninsult your acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...I got\Nso stressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's no excuse\Nfor what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have every right\Nto be upset with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not upset because\Nyou insulted my acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because in all the time\Nwe've known each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd taught you about\Nthe importance of friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,trust, and honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't fly away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies are taking their\Nseats for the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. Standing\Nroom only!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do a good job\Nof advertising
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,for this thing or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't put on a show\Nwith no lead actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You go find Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll figure out a way to stall\Nthis thing till you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony's gonna volunteer\Nto try to tame that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,NoPONY indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So... ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[ahem] Er. Who likes juggling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!\NCan we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I haven't\Nmuch to say, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You've guided me\Nsince I was a filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've given me knowledge,\Nand advice, and friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be able to\Ngive something back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I did was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've told you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I promised you\Ncould be in our play!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing would make me feel worse\Nthan knowing I disappointed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I look up to you more than\Nanypony I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to let you down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,like I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] You had good\Nintentions, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know that the\Ntruth is always better
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,than a well-meant lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Applejack remind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,About a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, because I\Ndidn't listen to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've ruined your\Nwhole Onesversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't\Nknow about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there an old saying,\N"The show must go on"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be a way for\Nus to save the play yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if I'm being\Ncompletely honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but I am a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,BOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good news, free food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad news?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This play is\Nofficially a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, I know\Na thing or two
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,about how to deal\Nwith those.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But let's celebrate later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we have a show to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But-but-but how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The audience is\Nabout to riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no backdrop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And our lead actress is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No longer in that role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, Applejack, Pinkie Pie,\NTwilight, go calm the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them know the play will\Nstart in just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, bring\Nus some clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and place them\Nbehind the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There. That's our\Nnew backdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, do you have\Na copy of the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you\Nnarrate the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy will\Nbe our new lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Playing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,While you watch me playing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, oh no, I think my\Nstage fright is coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Visualize with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Regal, commanding,\Nconfident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the rising\Nsun's warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Once upon a time,\Nbefore Celestia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria was suffering\Nterrible hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Raising the sun every\Nmorning was so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that it took five\NUnicorn Sorcerers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,plus Starswirl the\NBearded to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You call THOSE\Ngreat sorcerers? Ha! Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Hecklers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Improvise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! And... uh...raising the sun\Neach day was super-draining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can see that\Nfor yourselves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, do these guys\Nlook beat up or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Starswirl's so stressed\Nhe's got kinks in his horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause it turns out, Celestia\Nhad the special power
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to raise the sun\Nall by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for a new\Nday in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[music flourish\Nand then silence]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! In all the commotion, we\Nforgot we don't have a sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We play Charades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [majestic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea this production
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,would have such elaborate\Nspecial effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by how many\Nflowers the audience threw,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems our play was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel bad you never got\Na chance to actually be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I never felt I had to be on\Nstage to be a part of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All I ever wanted was to share\Nan honest bond of creativity,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,artistry, and happiness\Nwith my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly\Nwhat I got to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving our\Nplay, Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But from now on, none of you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,will have to call me\N"Princess" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I had so much fun\Ntonight, I've decided
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to give up my crown, step\Ndown from the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and devote all of my\Ntime to the theatre!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You...WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm not such a\Nbad actress, after all.
